# meraki_wireless_ethernet_port_profile_default (Resource)

This resource can manage the `Wireless Ethernet Port Profile Default` configuration.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "meraki_wireless_ethernet_port_profile_default" "example" {
  network_id = "L_123456"
  profile_id = "1001"
}
```
